SOURCE: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/docs/self-hosting/apps/install-apps/zoho.mdx#2025-04-20_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
<Cal.com URL>/api/integrations/zohocrm/callback
```

